HIV-1 infection of renal epithelial cells: 30 years of evidence from transgenic 
animal models, human studies and in vitro experiments.

Blasi M(1)(2)(3), Klotman M(4)(5)(6).

Author information:
(1)Department of Medicine, Division of Infectious Diseases, Duke University 
School of Medicine, Durham, NC, USA. maria.blasi@duke.edu.
(2)Duke Human Vaccine Institute, Duke University School of Medicine, Durham, NC, 
USA. maria.blasi@duke.edu.
(3)Duke University Medical Center, MSRBII Room 3077, Durham, NC, 27710, USA. 
maria.blasi@duke.edu.
(4)Department of Medicine, Division of Infectious Diseases, Duke University 
School of Medicine, Durham, NC, USA. mary.klotman@duke.edu.
(5)Duke Human Vaccine Institute, Duke University School of Medicine, Durham, NC, 
