Cardiotoxicities of Novel Therapies in Hematologic Malignancies: Chimeric 
Antigen Receptor T-Cell Therapy and Bispecific T-Cell Engager Therapy.

Marar RI(1), Abbasi MA(2), Prathivadhi-Bhayankaram S(3), Daryanani A(2), 
Villarraga H(2), Anavekar N(2), Bhatt VR(1), Paludo J(4).

Author information:
(1)Division of Hematology-Oncology, University of Nebraska Medical Center, 
Omaha, NE.
(2)Division of Cardiovascular Medicine, Mayo Clinic, Rochester, MN.
